storyInfo: Under Fumizuki's orders, personal bodyguard Shirayuki joins Rhodes Island, and her first order of business upon is to investigate this company...

attributes.content: Yuki-chan.
attributes.name: Fumizuki

attributes.content: Here.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: I've informed Yenwu. Now, I've arranged for you to enter a pharmaceutical company called Rhodes Island as an operator.
attributes.name: Fumizuki

attributes.content: Rhodes Island?
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Yes. You've likely already heard of it.
attributes.name: Fumizuki

attributes.content: Only that the Miss has deep ties with them.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Does the Princess want me to protect the Miss?
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Hm... that has been part of my intent. After all, this is an Infected organization. However, I believe Hui-chieh should be able to handle things herself.
attributes.name: Fumizuki

attributes.content: Infected... does the Princess consider them reliable?
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Yes. Be assured. I've met their leader before. She is quite a good girl.
attributes.name: Fumizuki

attributes.content: And I've looked into things a little. I feel the company itself is good too. So, I feel this is a good opportunity.
attributes.name: Fumizuki

attributes.content: Opportunity?
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Yes. You've followed me since childhood. Even now in Lungmen, you haven't once left my side.
attributes.name: Fumizuki

attributes.content: It is my mission.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: But you also ought to see the sights outside.
attributes.name: Fumizuki

attributes.content: I need only to know what sights the Princess sees.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: This is an order, Yuki-chan.
attributes.name: Fumizuki

attributes.content: ...Understood.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: I am Shirayuki. Princess Fumizuki told me to assist Madam Ch'en and follow all your orders.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Several days' observation. The Doctor, a strange sort.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Directly heats instant food in mouth with kettle. Genius.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: But holds true requisite ability, in command of people and handling of sundry affairs.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Further, Rhodes Island. More than meets the eye.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Surface-level, a pharmaceutical company. In reality, close to a military organization. With fair strength. No surprise Lord Wei would cooperate with this company.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: The Princess spoke it not forth, but as Miss Ch'en is here, I am presumably willed to investigate this organization, and protect the Miss in full.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Doctor aside, two others are leaders here.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Amiya, I have met. In the Princess's words, a very kindly person.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: But as she has proven a leader, exceptionality must reside. Cannot be taken lightly.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: The other, a Kal'tsit, not yet met. From others' conversation, the true core figure of this company. Further understanding of her required.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Rough structure of accessible ship interior area committed to memory. Time, one in the morning. I shall move out.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Entered.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Rhodes Island's pipeline design, adequate.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Ordered systematically, omnidirectional... and correspondingly monitored.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: But such levels, a mere trifle.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Most passages are connected with dormitories via toilets. Only some windows give sight of what happens within dormitories, due to planning... Fair.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Hwaaah... Gummy, I wanna eat meat...
Ceobe.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Abysmal sleeping posture.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Phew... Wonderful. That's enough training today to hit standards.
attributes.name: Midnight

attributes.content: It's late now. Though there are no missions tomorrow, I should quickly do my skincare, and then it's beddy-byes.
attributes.name: Midnight

attributes.content: Ah. Ever since I became an Operator, I haven't been properly managing my appearance.
attributes.name: Midnight

attributes.content: But what can you do? Some things are a necessary sacrifice.
attributes.name: Midnight

attributes.content: And I suppose even if I don't take care, I'm handsome enough as is.
attributes.name: Midnight

attributes.content: (Shudder)
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Operator codename, Midnight.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Narcissist.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Yet, ample muscle definition.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Hm? Is it already this late?
attributes.name: Dobermann

attributes.content: Whatever. Just a bit longer. I'm almost done drawing up the training program for Kroos's group.
attributes.name: Dobermann

attributes.content: Kids really mature fast, don't they? You wouldn't recognize them now compared to when they just arrived at Rhodes Island.
attributes.name: Dobermann

attributes.content: Heh. Though they're still a mile from where I want them to be.
attributes.name: Dobermann

attributes.content: Instructor Dobermann.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Steel-cold, heart of gold.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Most have already fallen asleep.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Rhodes Island's people by and large, seem used to life here.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Just as the Princess's words, a good place.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Ahead leaves the dormitory area. Tread carefully.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: *Pant*... *pant*...
attributes.name: Rosa

attributes.content: Natalya... uh, should be calling you Rosa now. About time you call it.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Phew... You go to bed first. I'll do a little more training by myself.
attributes.name: Rosa

attributes.content: ...Fine. You've got me for a while longer.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: I let you live. Think how bad I'd look if you just went and bit it on the battlefield.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Aha. If I could trouble you, then.
attributes.name: Rosa

attributes.content: Two students from Ursus. Seemingly, refugees admitted prior.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Chernobog. A tragedy.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: I wish you good luck.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Hm? That...
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Amiya, we'll conclude our work for today here.
attributes.name: Kal'tsit

attributes.content: Alright, Dr. Kal'tsit.
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: I'm not sure if the Doctor's asleep yet. I'll go and take a quick look.
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Dr. {@nickname} possesses a peculiar set of norms.
attributes.name: Kal'tsit

attributes.content: That might be true, but the Doctor's wellbeing is also very important!
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: I'll turn in after I've checked on the Doctor. Is that alright, Dr. Kal'tsit?
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: ...Suit yourself.
attributes.name: Kal'tsit

attributes.content: Mm-hm!
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: So this should be Dr. Kal'tsit...
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Her gaze, as though it flickered hither! Have I been found?!
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: (Seemingly, she has not noticed me. Yet that sensation, it was...)
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Forget it. As I am not found, I shall proceed.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: (Hm? Ahead, an impression of great noise... surmising from direction, likely the Engineering Department.)
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Wait wait wait! No way! You're meant to kiss right freaking here, aren't you?! What are you hesitating for?! You're the heroine!
attributes.name: Closure

attributes.content: Ugh, come on, one of these scenes is enough! Don't do it every time! What's your PROBLEM, scriptwriter?!
attributes.name: Closure

attributes.content: Euuugh, I haaate this kind of development... How are they on their seventh season by now? And the reviews get crappier each time.
attributes.name: Closure

attributes.content: They're just dragging it out! That's all they're doing!
attributes.name: Closure

attributes.content: ...Dammit, but that boy's so hot. And he's in every episode!
attributes.name: Closure

attributes.content: Fine. I'll hang in there. Can't say it won't get better!
attributes.name: Closure

attributes.content: Chief Engineer Closure.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: 'Tis alleged that the Rhodes Island ship was her plan alone. Fearsome.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Yet this is not where the show's true ruin lies. The fourth season's spontaneous introduction of the supporting man; such was a nightmare.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: What? You're kidding me?! I thought this was bad enough!
attributes.name: Closure

attributes.content: ...You catch upon my words?!
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Oh, shoot, I knee-jerked that one out.
attributes.name: Closure

attributes.content: Whatever, come down here.
attributes.name: Closure

attributes.content: ...Since when?
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: The start.
attributes.name: Closure

attributes.content: Oh, don't get me wrong, your ninja techniques are real amazing stuff. Thing is, I just knew you were gonna do this from the start.
attributes.name: Closure

attributes.content: ...'Twas my individual action, untied to anyone.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Alright, alright, loosen up. You think I'm treating you as a spy here or something?
attributes.name: Closure

attributes.content: Princess Fumizuki specially phoned up Amiya when she sent you over.
attributes.name: Closure

attributes.content: When she did, she told Amiya, even if she had no ulterior motive sending you here, she was worried you might go a little overboard. So, she specifically warned us beforehand to keep our ears perked.
attributes.name: Closure

attributes.content: And she gave Amiya a couple details on your MO, so I've been a little extra aware of you the past while.
attributes.name: Closure

attributes.content: ...This has naught to do with the Princess.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Jeez, you are some tough customer.
attributes.name: Closure

attributes.content: Y'know, now I get the feeling I can't really talk you over.
attributes.name: Closure

attributes.content: But if we actually treated you like a spy, wouldn't Kal'tsit have just dealt with you back there?
attributes.name: Closure

attributes.content: Basically, seeing as this is your first offense, don't you worry that anyone's gonna punish you, or that it'll reflect badly on your Princess.
attributes.name: Closure

attributes.content: But I don't recommend you try prowling around Rhodes Island like that again.
attributes.name: Closure

attributes.content: On the one hand, you'd absolutely, aaaaaabsolutely never get into the core. At least, the pipes won't let you.
attributes.name: Closure

attributes.content: But on the other hand, snooping into other people's privacy isn't super cool.
attributes.name: Closure

attributes.content: And don't you get tired doing that?
attributes.name: Closure

attributes.content: I do not.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: I will not repeat this.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: And you're gonna go find some other way instead, aren't you?
attributes.name: Closure

attributes.content: ...I make no guarantee.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Wowie, do I wanna let Kal'tsit sic you. Loyal people are such a pain in the neck, honestly.
attributes.name: Closure

attributes.content: But whatever, Kal'tsit wanted me to tell you this instead. 'You may use your methods to observe Rhodes Island, but Rhodes Island is observing you too.'
attributes.name: Closure

attributes.content: ...I understand.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Hey, honestly, if you're so bored at night you wanna roam around, you can come watch these stories with me.
attributes.name: Closure

attributes.content: You gave me the impression you've done a little research into them. Most of Rhodes Island are all outdoorsy types, and I'm starving for any compatriots of my own. It's killing me, c'mon.
attributes.name: Closure

attributes.content: In continuing to watch this, you will truly find no value.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: I may recommend some. I know not if you possess them.
attributes.name: Shirayuki

attributes.content: Alright, alright!
attributes.name: Closure

attributes.content: Lay 'em on me, and if I don't have them, I'll go find them for us to watch together!
attributes.name: Closure

attributes.content: ...Very well.
attributes.name: Shirayuki
